Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kamu mau menyoraki kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan sangat senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya menganggap mereka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai teman yang penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka penting bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyoraki mereka dulu!
