Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dia juga tidak ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soo-Sooha, dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak akan\Nmembiarkan kalian menang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menang demi Sooha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sebuah gol penentuan!\N- Khan, kamu hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sekolah Kota Sunshine\N- Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- berhasil membalas kekalahan!\N- Sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sekolah Kota Sunshine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa terjadi sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Anda bersama Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang membawanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sang leluhur, Dardan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sang leluhur, Dardan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kalian benar-benar\Ntidak ingat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dardan adalah\NKanselir Kerajaan Vargr kuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya dia hanya manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi untuk mendapatkan kekuatan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menggunakan sihir terlarang\Ndan mengubah dirinya menjadi vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sudah bertemu dengannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyerang kami\Ndengan gerombolan vampir sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makhluk apa yang dia bawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka vampir tingkat rendah\Nyang diciptakan oleh Dardan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak punya ketahanan\Nterhadap sinar matahari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka juga sangat tidak rasional.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka juga tidak bisa\Nmenahan rasa haus darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tahu itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berbeda dari para vampir itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kalian adalah bangsawan vampir\Ndari Kerajaan Vargr kuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangsawan vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian juga kesatria\Nyang melayani putri kerajaan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang akan percaya\Npada orang yang memenjarakan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak memenjarakan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menempatkan kalian\Ndi Panti Asuhan Vamfield
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk melindungi kalian dari Dardan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih dari seribu tahun lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat kerajaan itu putus asa\Nkarena pemberontakan Dardan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sang Putri mengirim jiwa kalian
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke masa depan untuk melindungi kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalian kehilangan ingatan\Ndari masa itu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menjadi bayi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukan kalian semua
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bawa kalian ke Panti Asuhan Vamfield\Nuntuk dilindungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, mungkinkah putri itu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengikuti energi sang Putri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan akhirnya menemukan tempat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kalian semua\Nsecara naluriah menyadari
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa takdir kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu apa tujuan Dardan menculik Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menginginkan kekuatan sang Putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, semuanya milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri. Dardan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri, Anda di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti tentang masalah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, pangeran kerajaan tetangga\Ndatang dan melamarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, saya sudah mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar dia sosok yang mengagumkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku belum ingin menikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka ingin aku mengabdikan hidupku\Nuntuk orang yang tak kukenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku tak ditakdirkan\Nmencintai orang yang kuinginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya yakin Anda akan bertemu\Nseseorang yang Anda cintai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku harus memberi tahu Ibu\Ndengan jelas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Tuan Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu saja dibantu oleh Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tugas saya memang melindungi Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda juga tampak cantik\Ndan menawan hari ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Selen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana perkembangan\Nlamaran pernikahanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanselir Dardan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sudah menolaknya dengan hormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memang kabar baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka\NAnda akan mengikuti keinginan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak ada hubungannya denganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Anda,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya juga menentang pernikahan politik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda menguping pembicaraanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara Anda selalu terdengar oleh saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengenai alasannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena seluruh hati saya\Nhanya untuk Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurang ajar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurang ajar, katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa karena saya bukan keturunan kerajaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Anda masih saja memandang status.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lepaskan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan\Nuntuk memenangkan hatimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dardan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau berani kasar kepada Tuan Putri lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak akan membiarkanmu lolos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja, orang itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selen... Selen! Bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal yang kita takutkan ternyata terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan Syaman keluarga kerajaan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang diwariskan turun-temurun\Nadalah penyebabnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Putri Selen adalah\Norang terkuat dalam sejarah kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhnya tidak bisa lagi\Nmenahan kekuatan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan mati jika terus begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya ada satu cara\Nuntuk menyelamatkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gunakan harta kerajaan,\Ndarah Dewa Serigala Kuno Vargr,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk menyelamatkan nyawanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya hangat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Selen,\Nputri yang mewarisi kekuatan Syaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku, Vargr, Dewa Serigala,\Nakan memberimu kekuatanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Vargr...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selen, kamu sudah sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah, kamu baik-baik saja sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertemu Vargr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak, Vargr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selen, jangan sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pun tahu\Nkalau ini satu-satunya cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dardan, yang menjadi leluhur,\Ningin mengeklaim kerajaan ini sebagai miliknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan dengan bantuan\Nkaum manusia serigala,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita masih kalah jumlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kamu harus\Nberbagi darahmu dengan orang lain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menciptakan bangsawan vampir baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersama mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lindungi kerajaan ini dari Dardan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku masih...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah meminum darah Vargr,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mendapatkan kekuatan Dewa Serigala Kuno,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menjadi Ratu Vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, kamu akan mewarisi\Nkekuatan Syamanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menyegel semua kekuatanku\Ndi Altar Darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selen, setelah aku mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu harus pergi ke Altar Darah\Nuntuk upacara suksesi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hancurkan segelnya\Ndan serap kekuatan ratu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk menjadi ratu terkuat dalam sejarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir, Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya yang akan mewarisi kekuatan itu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memerintah kerajaan ini dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dardan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Selen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya juga tidak mau melakukan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya hanya menginginkan cintamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua salahmu karena tidak menatapku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku hanya bisa membawamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski harus menghancurkanmu,\Naku akan menjadikanmu milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lindungi Tuan Putri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli, selamatkan Tuan Putri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri, Anda baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dardan, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menghalangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga mencintai Tuan Putri,\Njadi kamu pasti mengerti perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nseharusnya kamu setuju denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, semuanya milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri, pergilah ke Altar Darah.\NCepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marge, punggungmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus menyelesaikan upacara suksesi\Nsecepat mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang berkorban
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}agar aku menjadi ratu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marge, aku punya permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan kembali ke istana sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mengirim jiwa Tuan Heli\Ndan yang lainnya ke masa depan yang jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, saat waktunya tepat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tolong cari mereka semua\Ndan lindungi mereka dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani sekali kamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asalkan untukmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya bersedia melakukan\Nhal yang lebih buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang merepotkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda selalu melindungiku\Ndari banyak kesulitan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak pernah takut apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda juga tidak pernah ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu Anda menyembunyikan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku juga menyembunyikan\Nperasaan itu di hatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, saat kita bertemu lagi nanti,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuharap kita bisa saling jujur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Dardan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mencoba mencuri kekuatan Syaman\Ndan Vargr milik Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, legenda itu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, di Episode 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bulan Berkabut: Kabut Hitam Railgun.
